Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    The current Board, it contains the tiles and items in the level.
    Maze_Impl
    Implements the Maze interface and is the point of interaction between the maze logic and the application.
    MazeState_Impl
    Implements the MazeState interface and describes the state of a maze (a level) including the board, items, chap, and enemies.
    NullMaze
    Represents and empty maze.
    NullMazeState
    Represents an empty maze description.
